title: Love Destiny
overview: Five years ago, Su Xiaohuan and Xiao Mo fell in love with each other, while rumors began to spread that Xiao Mo was engaged to the star Gu Jing. They never confessed to each other. Su Xiao han went to France, continued to study design and received many awards. One day, Su Xiaohuan gets a chance to participate in the BRD jewelry design competition. After returning home, she went to Mingzuanfang jewelry store, whose boss turned out to be Xiao Mo. The year Su Xiaohuan left, Xiao Mo tried to find her, but in vain, and founded the Mingzuanfang jewelry brand, waiting for the return of his beloved.
